## Calcium Channel — MCP-over-qrexec access control
## Managed by calciumchannel.McpRegister or manually.
##
## Format: calciumchannel.Mcp +<server>  <source-vm>  <mcp-vm>  allow autostart=yes
##
## Discovery service — any VM can list its own allowed servers
calciumchannel.McpList      *  @anyvm       @adminvm  allow
calciumchannel.McpRegister  *  ADMIN_VM     @adminvm  allow
calciumchannel.McpRegister  *  @anyvm       @adminvm  deny

## Per-server rules are appended below by McpRegister
